body
  .container
    .jumbotron.text-center
      .logo
        a(href="https://sas.utmn.ru")
          img(src="/assets/logo_sas_ut_short-red.svg")
      h1 Feedback. Year 2019â€“2020. Quarter 3. ESL.
      h3 Course evaluations are to be filled in ENGLISH only. 
      h3 Please note that the use of the scoring system 0, 5 and 10 is only a recommendation, you can use any indicator from 0 to 10.     
      form(id="form" action="/polls/feedback-collector" method="post")
        input(type="hidden" value="ba_2019_q3_esl" name="subject")
        fieldset   
          div(class="input-group")
            .flex-container
              label(for="Who taught this course") Who was the instructor for this course?
              select(class="form-control" required="required" name="Who taught this course")
                option(value="Irina Parakhina") Irina Parakhina
                option(value="Anna Syrchina") Anna Syrchina
                option(value="Valeria Evdash") Valeria Evdash
                option(value="Tatyana Kovaleva") Tatyana Kovaleva
            .flex-container
              label(for="To what extent was this course an improvement over English language courses you have had previously") To what extent was this course an improvement over English language courses you have had previously? Give a score from 1 to 10, where 1 = It is not helping at all and 10 = It is helping significantly.
              input(type="number" required="required" class="form-control" name="To what extent was this course an improvement over English language courses you have had previously" min="1" max="10")
            .flex-container
              label(for="In what ways was this course useful in terms of improving your English language skills") In what ways was this course useful in terms of improving your English language skills? Put your thoughts.
              textarea(required="required" class="form-control" name="In what ways was this course useful in terms of improving your English language skills" rows="4")
            .flex-container
              label(for="If you had the chance to change some aspects of the course what would they be?") If you had the chance to change some aspects of the course what would they be? Put your thoughts.
              textarea(required="required" class="form-control" name="If you had the chance to change some aspects of the course what would they be?" rows="4")
            .flex-container
              label(for="To what extent did the instructors focus on speaking skills?") To what extent did the instructor focus on speaking skills? Put your thoughts.
              textarea(required="required" class="form-control" name="To what extent did the instructor focus on speaking skills?" rows="4")
            .flex-container
              label(for="To what extent did the instructors focus on grammar skills?") To what extent did the instructor focus on grammar skills? Put your thoughts.
              textarea(required="required" class="form-control" name="To what extent did the instructor focus on grammar skills?" rows="4")
        button(type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg") Submit
